NAME
    introspect - show summary of all models with fields and record counts

SYNOPSIS
    introspect [model]

DESCRIPTION
    Displays a summary of all models in the database, including:
    - Model name and total record count
    - User-defined fields (excludes system fields)
    - Field types and required markers

    System fields excluded: id, created_at, updated_at, access_read,
    access_edit, deleted_at

    Required fields are marked with an asterisk (*).

OPTIONS
    model
        Show only the specified model. If omitted, shows all models.

EXAMPLES
    introspect
        Show all models with their fields and counts

    introspect users
        Show only the users model

OUTPUT FORMAT
    model_name (N records)
      - field_name*: type
      - field_name: reference(other_model)

SEE ALSO
    describe, select, count
